<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <title><%= title || 'Help Center' %> - BambiSleep.Chat</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pages/docs.css">
    <% if (typeof fileName !== 'undefined') { %>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/highlight.css">
    <% } %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav', { path: '/help' }) %>
    
    <div class="container docs-container">
        <aside class="docs-sidebar">
            <h3>Documentation</h3>
            <ul class="docs-list">
                <li><a href="/help/USER-GUIDE" class="doc-link">📖 User Guide</a></li>
                <li><a href="/help/API" class="doc-link">🔌 API Documentation</a></li>
                <li><a href="/help/DETAILS" class="doc-link">🏗️ Technical Details</a></li>
            </ul>
        </aside>
        
        <section class="docs-content">
            <% if (typeof fileName !== 'undefined' && typeof content !== 'undefined') { %>
                <div class="docs-header">
                    <h2><%= title %></h2>
                </div>
                <div class="markdown-body">
                    <%- content %>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="help-header">
                    <h1>🧠 BambiSleep.Chat Help Center</h1>
                    <p>Your guide to BambiSleep.Chat features and documentation</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="help-container">
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>🚀 Quick Start</h2>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Enter your Bambi name when prompted</li>
                            <li>Navigate to the main chat interface</li>
                            <li>Use the "Prompt my AIGF" textarea to interact</li>
                            <li>Watch for audio triggers and responses</li>
                            <li>Level up to unlock advanced features</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>🤖 AIGF Interaction</h2>
                        <p>The core feature of BambiSleep.Chat is the AIGF (AI Generated Fantasy) interaction system:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Prompt Interface:</strong> Use the main textarea with "Prompt my AIGF" to send messages</li>
                            <li><strong>Real-time Responses:</strong> Receive instant AI-generated responses</li>
                            <li><strong>Audio Integration:</strong> Automatic audio playback based on trigger words</li>
                            <li><strong>Profile Awareness:</strong> AI adapts responses based on your Bambi profile and level</li>
                            <li><strong>Eye Cursor:</strong> Special visual feedback system during interactions</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>💡 Key Features</h2>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>AIGF Chat:</strong> Interactive AI conversations with personalized responses</li>
                            <li><strong>Bambi Name System:</strong> Personal identity management for customized experiences</li>
                            <li><strong>Audio Triggers:</strong> Hypnotic audio activation based on keywords and context</li>
                            <li><strong>Profile System:</strong> Level progression and feature unlocking</li>
                            <li><strong>Real-time Interface:</strong> Live socket-based communication</li>
                            <li><strong>Visual Effects:</strong> Eye cursor and interactive visual elements</li>
                            <li><strong>Control Systems:</strong> Advanced customization and trigger management</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>📋 Documentation</h2>
                        <div class="docs-cards">
                            <div class="doc-card">
                                <h3><a href="/help/USER-GUIDE">📖 User Guide</a></h3>
                                <p>Complete guide for using BambiSleep.Chat</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="doc-card">
                                <h3><a href="/help/API">🔌 API Documentation</a></h3>
                                <p>Technical API reference for developers</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="doc-card">
                                <h3><a href="/help/DETAILS">🏗️ Technical Details</a></h3>
                                <p>System architecture and implementation</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </section>
    </div>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
